Wordle 434 is the challenge that has gone live for Saturday August 27. If you've tried guessing the answer for the daily Wordle today but have been left a bit stumped then Express Online is here to help. We've got some hints and meaning tips to help you figure out the answer to Wordle 434. If you're not already aware, Wordle is an online word game that has taken the world by storm during the past year. Each day a new five letter word is added to the Wordle website, with players getting six guesses to figure it out. Answers are entered into a tiled grid and each tile flashes a different colour depending on whether you're spot on or not. If the letter you entered is correct and in the right position a tile will go green, if the letter you entered is in the Wordle answer but not in the right position it will go yellow and if the letter isn't in the word at all the tile will go grey. This colour coded system lets people share online their route to figuring out an answer without giving any spoilers away. People who managed to guess the daily Wordle answer for today in one go will be able to share the coveted social media post which shows one row of six green squares. What a clever clogs! If you're having trouble with the latest daily Wordle - Wordle 434 - which is out on Saturday August 27 then Express Online has rounded up some tips to help below. We've got some general Wordle tips and tricks followed by specific guidance for Wordle 434 below... General Wordle tips and tricks... • Don't use the same letter twice in your opening guess. • Try to use a couple of vowels in your first guess, particularly 'A' and 'E'. • Avoid letters such as 'X', 'Z' and 'Q' until later on, when you have a better idea what the answer is. • 'RAISE' is a good word to start with, while 'TOUCH' is a decent second guess. • Check out the daily hints provided by Express Online below... Wordle 434 hints and clues for August 27... 1. Wordle 434 starts with the letter R. 2. Wordle 434 contains two vowe